aWFRuleDesc.RuleText:
; aWF_RT_Formule (aWLIClaimRuleEngineWithCashValue) (Def Version:1) (Implem Version:1)
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Num8) switch self.Subscriber__Age__Exact when 0 to 40 Result = 250 endWhen when 41 to 45 Result = 215 + 7 * (45 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 46 to 50 Result = 185 + 6 * (50 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 51 to 55 Result = 150 + 7 * (55 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 56 to 60 Result = 130 + 4 * (60 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 61 to 65 Result = 120 + 2 * (65 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 66 to 70 Result = 115 + (70 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 71 to 75 Result = 105 + 2 * (75 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen when 76 to 90 Result = 105 endWhen when 91 to 95 Result = 100 + (95 - self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endWhen else Result = 100 endSwitch if self.Coverage__CoverageAmount < self.Option__CashValue * Result / 100 Result = self.Option__CashValue * Result / 100 else Result = self.Coverage__CoverageAmount endIf endProc
